Star jump
Released 3 September 2015 (Update)
Members No
Enhancer No
Duration 4.3 seconds
Requirements Completing the Drill Demon random event
Animation

Star jump is one of four exercise emotes unlocked as a Random event reward.

Upon completing a Drill Demon event, players are returned to their previous location in game, with a new exercise emote unlocked. Players cannot choose which of the four emotes unlock since this is random.

Upon use the player do five star jumps (also known as jumping jacks).
